			Battery
			A battery monitor
			by Dennis Tomas

Brief 
~~~~~ 
Battery is a simple battery monitor.

You need the acpi package to use it.

Installation
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Get Battery and its submodules from GitHub:

$ git clone --recursive https://github.com/dtomas/Battery.git

ROX
~~~
Drag the Battery app dir to a ROX panel.

XFCE
~~~~
Run the install script:

$ sudo python install_xfce.py

Then choose "Add New Items" from the panel menu and select Battery from the
list of items.

